text: Excellent, congratulations on completing part 1 of module 1. It's now time for me to check that you understand the principles we've dealt with in part 1. So answer the following questions. What will you do to be a part of the 5% who succeed at trading? Why do professional traders use volume profiling? And what is the difference and importance between subjective and objective analysis? Make sure you answer these questions first, and then next up we're going to practically apply the principles from part one.
